Name: UCSB
Description: A great university along the California Coast!

Name: Dodger Stadium
Description: A baseball park within the city of Los Angelas. I've been here with my father many times to watch the Dodgers play ball.

Name: Eiffel Tower
Description: An iconic tower within Paris. There are many tourists here. Amazing place

Name: Statue of Liberty
Description: A neoclassical sculpture on Liberty Island. A symbol of freedom in America. A light green structure that is very mesmerizing.

Name: Taj Mahal
Description: A religious landmark within India. It is extremely sacred place in Islam.

Name: Marina Bay Sands Hotel
Description: A famous hotel in Singapore with unique architecture. My family from the east lives near this. The ship on top is large and amazing.
